Magda Foy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Magda_Foy 0 Magda Foy (1905-2000), also known and often credited as "The Solax Kid", was a child actor in the silent film era who worked for Solax Studio, the largest pre-Hollywood studio in the United States from 1910 to 1913.
